              <li>"Would you like me to contact your HR department directly to confirm their policy?"</li>
            </ul>
          `;
          break;
        default:
          response = `
            <h4>Generic Response:</h4>
            <ul class="word-track-list">
              <li>"I understand your concern. Let me address that specifically."</li>
              <li>"This is a common question that many customers have. Let me explain how our program works."</li>
              <li>"That's a great point. Let me show you how novated leasing can actually help with this."</li>
            </ul>
          `;
